{"tid":2065222,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人明明唔係a0，但係真係唔想承認呢樣嘢","createTime":"2020-06-15T11:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T17:51:55.000Z","uid":325757,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7474e7c3ecad948cc78e8f02df7ad07baad8bd54","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚羞恥 簡直係我目前為止其中一個人生污點  點解會同舊垃圾一齊過 好想擺脫啊救命 完全唔知點解頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8d96174ef2fe99ab1f94ecac784d2d5e90fa6b","tid":2065222,"uid":9941,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"但係a0好煩<br />\na1都好<br />\na0啲人成日話你未試過唔知架啦<br />\n一係就點點點唔怪得你a0<br />\n總之咩都可以連去a0<br />\n明明就唔係咩特別<br />\n不過係社會認為人應該有伴"},{"pid":"13d15e1797b6581b2ff18b1ed1a676152302fd3e","tid":2065222,"uid":315852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"哇屌！我以為咁啱loop左落我個post到"},{"pid":"9a859cda0c7171a5e4098250c131e39028a0053c","tid":2065222,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7luXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=587442a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7luXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=d79781f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"a273da96e02883e74557296cc0e02a30f38fbd22","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c932c04d776b76113d729b5dd26d2aeee958e40d","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a273da96e02883e74557296cc0e02a30f38fbd22","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7815ca8e5708c3f2e7a5a34ae3aac8ae66cd7176","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c932c04d776b76113d729b5dd26d2aeee958e40d","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a273da96e02883e74557296cc0e02a30f38fbd22","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0efa34b4d29f9e1010c6d8faa80b86c0150304d","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7815ca8e5708c3f2e7a5a34ae3aac8ae66cd7176","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c932c04d776b76113d729b5dd26d2aeee958e40d","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a273da96e02883e74557296cc0e02a30f38fbd22","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"l