929f38e9e","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34890a4e19defe8309e3dc55fbec0d5d5e94a9ea","tid":2065222,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"自己性格獨立感好強，又唔係孤僻，又唔係內向，可能自細環境人事物影響導致我個人好鬼獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所有嘢都可以自己去面對去應付，<br />\n<br />\n即係心情煩惱都係自己可以take care，跟住空閒時間自己會有方向搵嘢做，有時好似仲好enjoy自己一個既時間，靜靜地咁思考。跟住有問題有唔識既嘢都係自己會處理到，會識點去搵到解決既方向，變相慢慢大個好多嘢都唔會假手於人，同埋變到無左果種搵人幫手/求人既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣既情況令到我好似無左果個搵另一半既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然因為周邊既人屢屢都開始拍拖，唔多唔少都會影響自己思維，覺得好似試下lor，點都試下啦，但當有機會果一刻就係唔知點解硬係過唔到自己果關，會覺得咁我又唔係十分鍾意佢，而且我又無需要有另一半響身邊既需要，做咩要投資精神落去開始一段感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家覺得自己性格好撚實際。"},{"pid":"e7cce61e6cf52e8031280c6414a9856757e99257","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20497391b45a3d980002c177db1397cb912d2c31","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4bb0c50147ef88596aab2501d0be2567b3e18ea","tid":2065222,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccac41117befa0ae06299bf10412b765a4d8eafc","tid":2065222,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gi